Trainers

Prebon grinned.

"Good. Now turn on your cloak we are going into this secretly. I will 
sneak up and install this claoking device on Spears. When we activate 
it, I will have Ignatius take her back to base and run tests to see 
if their would be a way to remove the Maximal chip without hurting 
her. The rest of us will than open fire on the Maximals. If Ramulus 
is there, you have my permission to do everything in your power to 
destroy him. Just try not to mutilate his body to badly. I need it to 
bring back an old friend. Now let's go!"

Prebon activated his cloak and took to the skies towards Spears. The 
other Trainers on Savage did the same.
